Package: refuginator
Title: An Interactive Tool for Identifying Refugia
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: person(given = "Nathaniel E. D.", family = "Morley", email = "nathaniel.morley2000@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre", "cph"), comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0005-3816-1023"))
Description: A shiny-based browser application for reconstructing organismal distributions 
    and identifying historical and geohistorical refugia using the methods
    published by Morley et al. (2026) <doi:10.1038/s43247-026-03563-3>.  
